text: The 2019 Tunisian Super Cup was the 14th edition of the Tunisian Super Cup, a football match contested by the winners of the 2017–18 Tunisian Ligue Professionnelle 1 and 2017–18 Tunisian Cup competitions. The match was played on April 1, 2019 at Abdullah bin Khalifa Stadium in Doha, Qatar. between 2017-18 Ligue 1 winners Espérance ST and 5th 2017-18 Ligue 1 CA Bizertin As an alternative to Club Africain 2017–18 Tunisian Cup winners., Esperance won the title for the fourth time in its history in the first edition since 18 years. ==Match== === Pre-match === ===Summary=== == Match details == {|
